h3. Summary
When viewing the *System Dashboard* as an admin user, having the *Activity Stream* in maximized mode will enable the *Edit* option on the dropdown menu.

h3. Steps to Reproduce
# Log in as an JIRA System Administrator;
# Navigate to the *System Dashboard*;
# Click on the *Maximize* icon on the *Activity Stream* gadget;
# After the window is maximized, click on the arrow pointing down to access the dropdown menu, and the *Edit* option will be available;

h3. Expected Results
Only the *Minimize* and *Refresh* options should be available.

h3. Actual Results
The *edit* option will be available. Using this option to make changes to the gadget's filters and options will apply these changes, which will be reverted back once the page is reloaded.

h3.Workaround
Use the page to *Configure System Dashboard* page to make changes to the gadgets. Changes made through this page will be kept after being saved.

